720093f-c.text:
(1)
Grand Street, at, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of Eldridge Street. Also shown is Eldridge Street, at and adjoining the N.E.
corner of Grand Street.
April 8, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, showing a closer view of Nos. 292-294 Grand Street, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of Eldridge Street. No. 294
is a frame house.
April 7, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
The same, showing a further view eastward. Note Elevated Station
of the Second Ave. line on Allen Street.
May 14, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
